LOCATION:Meet in The Lobby
DESCRIPTION:Category: The Arts\nPrice: Free\nAvailability: 2 spots left\nSt
 atus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/173809
 \n\nlease join The 'Quin House Art Collection curator Kate Chertavian for 
 an art tour in celebration of Women's History Month that will journey thro
 ughout the 'House. We will gather in the Lobby for a deep dive on works by
  Julie Mehretu and Louise Nevelson. Then tour highlights by female artists
