BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:quin-event-179241@thequinhouse.com
DTSTAMP:20260326T084244Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T150000
SUMMARY: 90 Minutes of Innovation: The Hypergrowth Playbook with Jon McNeil
 l 
LOCATION:The Pub
DESCRIPTION:Category: ‘Quin Chat\nPrice: Free\nAvailability: 66 spots lef
 t\nStatus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/1
 79241\n\n1:00PM Program\, 2:30PM Networking\n\nWhat does it take to scale 
 companies that don’t just grow - but redefine industries?\n\nIn this spe
 cial edition of 90 Minutes of Innovation\, John Werner - venture capitalis
 t\, MIT lecturer\, and Forbes AI columnist - sits down with Jon McNeill\, 
 former President of Tesla and former Chief Operating Officer of Lyft\, for
  the Boston premier of his new book\, The Algorithm: The Hypergrowth Form
 ula That Transformed Tesla\, Lululemon\, General Motors\, and SpaceX.\n\nH
 aving helped lead Tesla through one of the most critical scaling phases in
  modern business\, McNeill brings a rare operator’s lens to hypergrowth.
  In The Algorithm\, he distills the repeatable system behind companies tha
 t achieve extraordinary scale\, drawing from firsthand experience and case
  studies across some of the most iconic organizations of our time.\n\nToge
 ther\, Werner & McNeill will explore the core framework behind The Algorit
 hm\, and how hypergrowth actually works\, alongside lessons from Tesla\, L
 ululemon\, General Motors\, and SpaceX. The conversation will also examine
  what leaders must do differently at each stage of scale\, how to align pr
 oduct\, people\, and process for exponential growth\, and why most compani
 es stall while a select few break through.\n\nExpect a fast-moving\, insig
 ht-dense conversation that bridges storytelling with execution\, offering 
 a rare window into the operating system behind some of the world’s most 
 transformative companies. From the front lines of hypergrowth to the bluep
 rint behind it - one stage\, one conversation\, not to be missed.\n\n*This
  event is complimentary and reserved for members\, plus one registered gue
 st.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/179241
CATEGORIES:‘Quin Chat
END:VEVENT
