 lable\nTime: 7 PM – 10 PM\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/e
 vents/177700\n\nEnd the evening with a nightcap in The Reading Room\, wher
 e The ‘Quin’s pastry team presents a beautifully curated dessert cart�
 ��an elegant procession of confections designed to delight.\n\nIndulge in 
 refined creations such as Honey Lavender Goat’s Milk Cheesecake\, Lemon 
 Blueberry Cake\, and Coconut Cream Tart\, alongside more decadent notes of
  Dark Chocolate Pistachio Tart and Salted Caramel Milk Chocolate Bon Bons.
  Playful touches like Strawberry Rose Choux Puffs and Carrot Cake French M
 acarons offer a whimsical finish.\n\nWith tableside service and a touch of
