SUMMARY:Easter Dining 
DESCRIPTION:Category: Holiday\nPrice: Free / Included\nStatus: Available\nT
 ime: 10:30 AM – 3 PM\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events
 /177702\n\nCelebrate the season with a refined brunch across The ’Quin H
 ouse. Enjoy a three-course prix fixe at Café Q\, featuring springtime fla
 vors like Maine Lobster Benedict and Rack of Lamb\; a vibrant Latin-inspir
 ed menu at Lunasol with Halibut\, Lamb Birria\, and classic Huevos Rancher
 os\; or a Japanese-inspired feast at Bondo with sushi\, raw bar selections
 \, and highlights like Australian Lamb Chop Yakimono and Black Cod.\n\nFor
  a more relaxed experience\, The Pub offers à la carte Easter specials\
 , from Leg of Lamb to Alaskan Halibut\, finished with a seasonal sweet fin
 ale.\n\nCafé Q | 3-Course Prix Fixe | $89* per person\, $36* per child\n
 \nLunasol | 3-Course Prix Fixe | $98* per person\, $36* per child\n\nBond
 o | Brunch Prix Fixe | $105* per person\, $36* per child\n\nThe Pub |�
 �Á la Carte Specials\n\n*Beverages\, taxes & club fees are not included. 
 Families celebrating with children ages 6-12 are invited to reserve brunch
  in Café Q\, The Pub\, Lunasol or Bondo. Dining cancellations less than 4
 8 hours in advance of service\, or no shows are subject to a 100% charge p
 er member/guest. Regular guest policies are in effect on this holiday.\n\n
 Make a Reservation.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/177702
CATEGORIES:Holiday
END:VEVENT
