DESCRIPTION:Category: Member Mixer\nPrice: $100.00 per person\nStatus: Wait
 list Only\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/175996\n\nJo
 in The ‘Quin House Managing Director\, Matthias Kiehm\, for an evening o
 f meaningful connections over a thoughtfully curated three-course dinner. 
 Enjoy expertly paired wines as you engage with fellow members\, guided by 
 conversation prompts designed to inspire deeper\, more memorable exchanges
 . This unique experience offers the perfect blend of great company\, engag
 ing dialogue\, and a menu crafted to delight the senses.\n\n*Tickets are $
 100 per person\, plus tax\, and are reserved for members only. Cancellatio
 ns within 72 hours of the event\, or failure to attend\, will be charged i
 n full. Please inform us of any dietary needs or restrictions by emailing 
 happening@thequin.com at least 72 hours before dinner service.
