DESCRIPTION:Category: Holiday\nPrice: Free / Included\nStatus: Available\nT
 ime: 5 PM – 10 PM\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/17
 7703\n\nWe invite our community of members to gather for an evening of tra
 dition\, conversation\, and a beautifully prepared Passover meal. The chef
  will present a selection of cherished holiday specials—rich with histor
 y\, flavor\, and the warmth of shared celebration. Indulge in time-honored
  dishes crafted with care\, from tender\, Slow-Braised Brisket to Matzah B
 all Soup and a perfectly prepared Mediterranean Branzino.\n\n*Please be mi
 ndful of The 'Quin's regular dining cancellation & no show policy\, a $25 
 fee per member/guest less than 24-hours in advance of service. Children ag
 es 6-12 are welcome to join when seated with a parent in Café Q on this d
 ay.\n\nMake a Reservation.
