SUMMARY:'Quin Suite: Celtics vs Hornets
LOCATION:Offsite: TD Garden
DESCRIPTION:Category: Sports & Games\nPrice: $404.67 per person\nAvailabili
 ty: 5 spots left\nStatus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhou
 se.com/events/172756\n\nClaim your seat in The ’Quin Suite (#524) at TD 
 Garden for the Celtics matchup against the Charlotte Hornets.\n\n All suit
 e ticket options include incredible views of the on-court action and light
  game day bites. Quench your evening cravings with a grazing spread of che
 ese & charcuterie\, mezze\, jumbo shrimp cocktail and seasonal snacks! The
  suite also offers an assortment of refreshments including wine\, beer\, s
 eltzer and soft drinks. Are you game?\n\n*A pair of 'Quin suite seats is a
 vailable for $941 total ($470.50 per ticket). Individual suite tickets are
  available for bar stool / standing access only\, offered at a reduced pri
 ce of $433 per ticket. Suite tickets are non-refundable and are non-transf
 erable. Members may purchase tickets for up to 3 guests and are required t
 o accompany them at all times. The suite is limited to those ages 16+ as a
  courtesy to fellow members.
