SUMMARY:de Gournay Watercolor Class: Friday Session I
LOCATION:The Muse
DESCRIPTION:Category: The Arts\nPrice: Free\nStatus: Waitlist Only\nEvent U
 RL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/177616\n\nDiscover the art of 
 watercolor in an intimate workshop with de Gournay\, the esteemed London-b
 ased atelier celebrated for its hand-painted wallpapers and dedication to 
 centuries-old decorative techniques. Founded on a reverence for tradition 
 and craftsmanship\, de Gournay has become synonymous with exquisitely deta
 iled\, bespoke interiors around the world.\n\nSet against the backdrop of�
 �Seasons of Love\, the custom mural that defines The Muse\, this experien
 ce invites members to engage more deeply with the artistry behind the wall
 s. Guided by Head Artist Evie Coley\, participants will draw inspiration f
 rom the Spring panel\, exploring its delicate motifs\, nuanced palettes\, 
 and layered storytelling.\n\nAn immersive and tactile experience\, the wor
 kshop offers a rare opportunity to translate de Gournay’s timeless craft
 smanship into your own watercolor compositions.\n\n*This event is complime
 ntary and reserved for members only. All materials will be provided\, and
  light bites and refreshments will be served.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/177616
CATEGORIES:The Arts
END:VEVENT
