 ce invites members to engage more deeply with the artistry behind the wall
 s. Guided by Head Artist Evie Coley\, participants will draw inspiration f
 rom the Spring panel\, exploring its delicate motifs\, nuanced palettes\, 
 and layered storytelling.\n\nAn immersive and tactile experience\, the wor
 kshop offers a rare opportunity to translate de Gournay’s timeless craft
 smanship into your own watercolor compositions.\n\n*This event is complime
 ntary and reserved for members only. All materials will be provided\, and
  light bites and refreshments will be served.
