 th Team ’Quin will receive financial support from The ’Quin Impact Fun
 d\, which is allocating $25\,000 to be shared among riders. Individual spo
 nsorship amounts will be determined based on the final number of participa
 nts.\n\nWe’re proud to continue our partnership with the Patriots Plate
 let Pedalers (PPP) Team. This year\, riders will register exclusively wi
