 ill be shared following form completion. \n\nInterested in riding this ye
 ar? Click here. Registration closes on April 15th\, 2026. \n\nPlease reac
 h out to The 'Quin Impact Fund team at impact@thequin.com  with any ques
 tions or concerns.
